data.description: REDUCED PRICE :Buyer’ Save money with this home  Charles County excise tax has been completely PAID.   Beautiful and Spacious interior 3 level 3 Bedroom 2.5 Bathroom townhome with a garage, finished basement located in Gleneagles Community. The Main level has a large, beautiful kitchen with upgraded cabinets, granite counter tops and a island w/overhang for stools. The upper level has a private master full bath, walk-in closet and full bath for 2nd and 3rd large bedrooms. The community has a pool and a club house. It is conveniently located less than 5 miles from plenty of shopping, restaurants, main commuter routes and so much more. Schedule your appointment TODAY!
